      "text": "We-- you had to be a certain age to see adult movies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, what they called adult movies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was nothing adult them them.",
